Media Validation Tools (MVT) NEWS -- summary of changes.  2014-02-27
Copyright (C) 2013-2014 Intel Corporation

Version 0.2.1 - 27.Feb.2014
* Add mvt_run helper tool to run a batch of tests
* Add tests configs for VP8 (63), VP9 (208) and H.264 AVC (250)
* Add support for planar YUV 4:2:2 and 4:4:4 formats
* Fix support for cropped frames in FFmpeg (vaapi)
* Fix number of scratch surfaces for FFmpeg (vaapi)

Version 0.2.0 - 18.Feb.2014
* Add support for high bit depts (>8-bit)
* Add JM Reference Software version 18.6 (H.264 AVC decoder)
* Add --benchmark option to disable hashing and download of VA surfaces
* Add --gen-output option to save the raw decoded frames into Y4M format

Version 0.1.0 - 14.Feb.2014
* Initial release
